                     <interp inst="t18090517-31-defend328" type="age" value="23"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t18090517-31-off170" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090517-31-off170" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18090517-31-off170" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18090517-31-cd171" type="crimeDate">15th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090517-31-off170 t18090517-31-cd171"></join>, a counterpane, value 1 l. 1 s. a pair of sheets, value 1 l. three table cloths, value 6 s. a shift, value 3 s. a great coat, value 2 l. three coats, value 6 l. three petticoats, value 10 s. a bedgown, value 3 s. a pair of sugar tongs, value 1 s. two yards of silk, value 6 s. two pair of gown sleeves, value 2 s. and five pieces of cloth, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18090517-31-victim330" type="victimName">
                           James Valentine 
                           Lindlar
                        <interp inst="t18090517-31-victim330" type="surname" value="Lindlar"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18090517-31-victim330" type="given" value="James Valentine"></interp>
